    <h2 class="sect-title">About Parkland </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">If you are looking for a relaxed lifestyle in the quiet and peaceful suburbs in Calgary,
                then Parkland is the ideal neighborhood for you to settle in. </p>
            <p class=" par-lg">This charming residential neighborhood in South East Calgary is surrounded by the Fish
                Creek
                Provincial Park on the west and south, the Bow Bottom Trail on the east, and the Canyon Meadows Drive on
                the north.</p>
        </div>
